
Generating IDL DataType and default DataReader
----------------------------------------------

qldds_gensrc.py generates OMG IDL DataType and default DataReader from QuantLibAddin/C++ XML function definitions.  This script is derived from QuantLib's gensrc and it requires locations of source directories of ObjectHander, GenSrc and QuantLibAddin that can be passed as command line arguments.

Assuming ObjectHander, GenSrc and QuantLibAddin source trees are located under $HOME on Unix or in their default locations on Windows

Unix:
-----
$ python qldds_gensrc.py --oh_dir=$HOME/ObjectHandler-1.12.0 --gensrc_dir=$HOME/gensrc-1.12.0 --qladdin_dir=$HOME/QuantLibAddin-1.12.0

